Hook still held his dammaged arm, waiting for Scavanger and Mixmaster,
when he began to hear something. His head turned over his shoulder, as
he looked up, to see the two new robot enter. Hook merely looked up at
thim with a bit of contempt. "We are no earthlings, we are
Cybertronians, and we aren't supposed to be here." he said, a bit upset.

Apeface neared MT. Fujy, and soared gracefully into the hole. His radar
had picked up to none Decepticons, so he was flying carefully. When he
turned the bend, and saw the two creatures, he transformed, Spasma
jumping out of the cockpit, and landing on Apeface's shoulder in his
Beastmode. "Wha, who you?" Apeface asked.
